## Design system — bespoke SaaS support-tool aesthetic

Target feel: Intercom/Zendesk-meets-modern-SaaS. Clean, trustworthy, efficient. NOT the dark gallery-wall portfolio look.

| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| Brand blue | `#1D6AE5` (primary CTA, bot bubble) |
| Brand dark | `#0F172A` (headings, nav) |
| Surface | `#F8FAFC` (page bg) |
| Card | `#FFFFFF` with `box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08)` |
| Accent teal | `#0D9488` (online status, success states) |
| Warn amber | `#D97706` (offline/wait states) |
| Text primary | `#1E293B` |
| Text muted | `#64748B` |
| Font headings | **Inter** (700/600) — Google Fonts |
| Font body | **Inter** (400/500) |
| Border radius | 12px cards, 20px chat bubbles, 8px inputs |
| Chat bubble — user | `#1D6AE5` bg, white text, right-aligned |
| Chat bubble — bot | `#F1F5F9` bg, `#1E293B` text, left-aligned |

