## File manifest (12 files)

```
public/demos/ai-chatbot-for-customer-support/
├── index.html          ← widget + chat UI (customer view)
├── admin.html          ← admin panel
├── style.css           ← shared design system
├── chat.js             ← main chat orchestrator
├── model-loader.js     ← WebLLM → Transformers.js → template fallback chain
├── rag.js              ← FAQ retrieval (embeddings or keyword fallback)
├── order-api.js        ← mock order lookup
├── escalation.js       ← ET hours + handoff flow
├── admin.js            ← KB editor + analytics + session viewer
├── analytics.js        ← event tracking (deflection, query log)
├── knowledge-base.json ← FAQ corpus (20+ entries: orders, shipping, returns, account)
└── orders.json         ← 10 mock orders with realistic status data
```

