## Requirement-to-feature traceability

| Client requirement | Demo feature | File(s) |
|---|---|---|
| FAQ answering with knowledge base | RAG retrieval + LLM response + source citations | rag.js, chat.js, knowledge-base.json |
| Order status lookup | `lookupOrder()` called inline during chat | order-api.js, orders.json |
| Human handoff + ET hours routing | Escalation button, hours check, ticket confirmation | escalation.js |
| Embeddable on website | iframe-ready index.html, no CORS issues (same-origin) | index.html |
| Zendesk integration (conceptual) | Simulated ticket card styled as Zendesk UI | escalation.js, style.css |
| US data handling norms | All processing client-side, no data leaves browser | model-loader.js (shown in UI) |
| Zero token cost | WebLLM in-browser; no API calls | model-loader.js |

