## Research integration (pre-researcher confirmed)

All 5 research questions answered. Key builder directives from research:

1. **WebLLM:** `import { CreateMLCEngine } from "https://esm.run/@mlc-ai/web-llm"` — model `Llama-3.2-1B-Instruct-q4f16_1-MLC` (879 MB VRAM, ~600-900 MB one-time download, cached in IndexedDB). ✅
2. **Transformers.js WASM:** Package RENAMED — use `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@huggingface/transformers@4.2.0/+esm`; instruction `onnx-community/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct` q4/wasm; embedding `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` fp32/wasm. `@xenova/transformers` is frozen/EOL — do NOT use. ✅
3. **Zendesk widget UI:** 380x520px panel, brand-color header, bot bubbles left (light gray), user bubbles right (brand blue), typing indicator (3-dot pulse), escalation card (amber), ticket confirmation card (green). ✅
4. **FAQ corpus:** 20-entry authentic corpus provided in pre-researcher.out — use verbatim in knowledge-base.json. ✅
5. **Widget UI patterns:** Launcher 56px circle bottom-right, `role="dialog"` on panel, `aria-live="polite"` on feed, mobile full-screen below 480px. ✅

**WASM inference is slow (~3-8s):** show streaming/typing indicator; never let the UI appear hung.

**Plan status: READY — all research integrated, build can proceed.**

