- risks: Qwen2.5-0.5B WASM slow in CI (~3-8s) — typing indicator required; `@huggingface/transformers` v4 pipeline API may differ slightly from v3 docs — builder should test pipeline call against confirmed snippet in pre-researcher.out; 600-900 MB WebGPU model download requires honest progress UX.
